Cell[TextData[{
 "We see that the probability of the event \"either 1 is in the sample or 2 \
is in the sample\" is not simply the sum of the individual probability that 1 \
is in the sample plus the probability that 2 is in it. The reason is that in \
adding ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"8", "/", "20"}], "+", 
    RowBox[{"8", "/", "20"}]}], TraditionalForm]]],
